then underneath 'System Variables' i have... [code]Variable name:PATH Variable Value:C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_05\bin;C:\Program Files\QuickTime\QTSystem\;C:\Program Files\Common Files\Adobe\AGL[/code] then... idk what this is... Please help. I haven't been able to run a client in ages -.- and i have been wanting to lately so i seriously want to fix it.
